    "4131218": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the Millelith",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "Wh—Who are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Jiayi sent us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "Oh... Thank you. If it weren't for your help, today may have ended quite differently."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What is it you're doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "I'm in charge of keeping the Lantern Rite safe. A lot comes out of the woodwork at this time of year, there are thieves around every corner."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "I encountered one during my patrol just now, so I called a few men and we pursued them out here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "Once we got here we decided to split up. I was searching this area."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "The thief seems to have made a clean getaway, and I sure didn't bank on these monsters being here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "I was just assessing whether it would be better to send for reinforcements, or find another way to disperse them... And that's when you showed up and dealt with them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "*sigh* And thank goodness. I don't know how long it would've taken for the others to get here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "Well, I need to get back to looking for that thief... But thanks for your help. Until next time..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait a second! We're not done here!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "Oh? Is there something else?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There's a suspicious character down at the harbor..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "Ugh, another one? *sigh* It's interminable..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "Right. When I get back, I'll get the other troops to be extra vigilant in the area."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinghuo",
                    "T": "*sigh* In the middle of the festival too. What are they up to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The locals must take all their tasty treats for granted by now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But for a poor traveler, all alone out in the wilderness, often forced to survive on nothing but the most mysterious of mushrooms..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "For you, the Lantern Rite is the most important of all festivals!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So let's go back to the place where we <color=#00E1FFFF>witnessed the shady-looking guy</color>."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon hears from patrol officers that criminals love to go back for another look at the crime scene after the event. Eh, it's a psychological thing, apparently."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But the crime hasn't even happened yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's why there's no time to lose! When there's highly flammable materials involved, once the crime happens it'll be too late!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
