    "4131222": {
        "Desc": "Report back to Jiayi",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jiayi",
                    "T": "Traveler, word spreads fast! We will keep watch over the thief, thanks for your help."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jiayi",
                    "T": "Looks like the Mingxiao Lantern will be ready soon. A critical juncture, we cannot afford the slightest interference."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "On the topic of keeping Lantern Rite safe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jiayi",
                    "T": "Rest easy, word was passed up the chain. Another group of very capable troops has been brought in."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jiayi",
                    "T": "They're dressed as ordinary citizens, you wouldn't notice them in the crowd. If anyone dares make a move, they'll be on them in an instant."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jiayi",
                    "T": "That's sorted then. You two get some rest, we'll take it from here. Enjoy Lantern Rite in peace!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... Paimon supposes that's taken care of, then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "If only Xiao were here to see the Mingxiao Lantern."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*sigh* Paimon wishes so too. Guess he won't make it this time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, do you remember what the inspiration for the Mingxiao Lantern was?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "An adeptus..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, with a name like... Skybracer, or something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Skybracer sounds right..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So if it's modeled on an adeptus, maybe Xiao would be interested this time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "On the day the Mingxiao Lantern is ready, we can meet him at <color=#00E1FFFF>Wangshu Inn</color> like he suggested, then try to persuade him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Even though he said you can see the Mingxiao Lantern from Wangshu Inn... We should get up close if we wanna get that festival atmosphere."
                }
            ]
        ]
    }
